{"about_the_game":"Hello everyone. I invite you to play The Proponent - a first-person horror that focuses on the atmosphere and the presentation of the story through the details. I tried to avoid the extreme, when the narrative is presented only through notes and audio files, although I decided not to leave the game without them, sometimes it is a really good way to tell a part of the story. <br><br><br>Something bad happened to the building in which the protagonist settled some time ago: the doors were sealed, the rooms were mixed together like a deck of cards. Strange creatures began to inhabit these places, few survivors trying to survive and get out<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2084430/extras/Uley.gif?t=1703675024\" /><br><br>Explore the premises. Skillfully use weapons and save ammunition<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2084430/extras/Reload.gif?t=1703675024\" /><br><br>Use the &quot;Mirror&quot; to see what is hidden from the ordinary eye<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2084430/extras/WhiteRLong.gif?t=1703675024\" /><br><br>Some creatures are better to avoid, others are worth interacting with<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2084430/extras/SpLap.gif?t=1703675024\" /><br><br><br>Get to the finals and learn more about the world the main character is in, save yourself<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2084430/extras/Head.gif?t=1703675024\" /><br><br>There are no saves in the game! If you are dead, you are reborn at the key point, but only while playing the game. This little experience (about 2 hours) is continuous.","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2084430/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1703675